content.rendered: Kami menyediakan Kamera CCTV dari G-Lenz G-Lenz GEIP-3281 untuk anda dalam kebutuhan sistem pemantauan keamanan. Kamera CCTV G-Lenz G-Lenz GEIP-3281 sangat efektif dalam menaga keamanan rumah / kantor / gedung / dlsb. Kamera CCTV G-Lenz G-Lenz GEIP-3281 adalah produkt terbaik karena sudah dibekali : Support IR-CUT, with ICR and automatic color change to achieve day/night function Resolution 2MP True Day/Night Auto AGC, AES, BLE show original colors 50dB noise reducer, clear image Introduce advanced H.264 HP video compression, achieving ultra low bit rate, superb high-definition picture quality Support HVR / NVR , Support Onvif 2.2 Plug and Play, multipe network cloud security and surveillance IP66 dustproof & waterproof certified
